import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import "./index.css"
import App from "./App"
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route,  } from "react-router-dom"

ReactDOM.render(
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Route path ='/' component={App} exact={true} />
        <App />
    </BrowserRouter>,
    document.getElementById("root")
)
